item.title: One day in Budapest, Hungary
item.description: So, you wanna see the beautiful city of Budapest and you do not have enough time. D and I had the same problem and D did not even want to be here just for a day, but I somehow managed to plan this trip and it went well. I am leaving Budapest right now for Vienna and I am writing this on a bus. Ha. There is no other place like Budapest!
